{"tid":2265772,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我係東京大學歷史系畢業，今日介紹日本武士名刀的特色同故事","createTime":"2020-10-31T17:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T20:09:11.000Z","uid":353419,"like":27,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3c4e151a470a1a927a0282e547e1d7bb1c90478e","tid":2265772,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:15:06.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">簡介: </span>日本刀有著精彩漫長的文化歷史, 唔同的名刀都係由古代名人打造, 當中包含住戰爭,神話,政治色彩, 好多名刀至今仍然安放係博物館, 俾後人參觀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/55/An_%C5%8C-sasaho_yari%2C_the_copy_of_Tonbogiri.JPG/150px-An_%C5%8C-sasaho_yari%2C_the_copy_of_Tonbogiri.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F5%2F55%2FAn_%25C5%258C-sasaho_yari%252C_the_copy_of_Tonbogiri.JPG%2F150px-An_%25C5%258C-sasaho_yari%252C_the_copy_of_Tonbogiri.JPG&h=d44c85bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.蜻蛉切<br />\n<br />\n蜻蛉切係有「戰國第一」之稱本多忠勝的專用武器，日本三名槍之一，係德川家的刀匠藤原正真打造，呢把刀身長55.6 cm，最大特點就係異常地輕，相傳本多忠勝係戰上拎住呢把槍，跑得異常地快，往往追上敵人打，故此佢叫蜻蛉切因為好似蜻蛉咁輕盈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=21m0jnd/1s84000640rppr43n3r5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D21m0jnd%2F1s84000640rppr43n3r5.jpg&h=ea91e358&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.村正妖刀<br />\n<br />\n佢係日本最邪惡的一把刀，係江户時代由名匠村正一族打造，相傳得德川家康的爺爺，同織田家作戰果陣，俾家臣阿部彌七郎用呢把刀差啲砍死左，當時德川家康係受咀咒的刀，會吸食人血，可見古代日本人認為有啲刀變成成妖怪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pjg5gVA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fpjg5gVA.jpg&h=967767ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3長船太刀<br />\n<br />\n名刀工長光的作品，長光係來自優秀刀匠家族----長船一族，呢班刀轉折落入唔到武將手上，包括室町末期將軍足利義輝，織田信長的手下奧平信昌，但當中最有名的使用者，莫過於係雜賀孫市，佢係雜賀眾的首領，好多人以為佢用鐵炮，以&quot;槍神&quot;聞名於世，但其實佢真正用的係長船太刀，據說佢用長船之後，威力會勁左3倍"},{"pid":"f097782d54d156f2ae459e9765989aca13af4906","tid":2265772,"uid":51148,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:17:00.000Z","msg":"係20%勁3倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5b3000376062d08d47d2d7038bbd99e2c278b3","tid":2265772,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:17:11.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"617bb3836145f83f4907712965f3d7e449423a79","tid":2265772,"uid":113335,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:17:59.000Z","msg":"仲有魚神 正宗 菊一呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:信長學返黎"},{"pid":"2ec7ed4de31d90770f7227f2eb11583031eedade","tid":2265772,"uid":149773,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8afff921ed8e166a91982262198ded24792f4ed2","tid":2265772,"uid":340729,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T88TWeZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT88TWeZ.gif&h=0c2917dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"adbcc81ddcbdd99be32b7bc160cc1d70c3f03b7d","tid":2265772,"uid":228894,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:19:44.000Z","msg":"蜻蛉切個名唔係因為鋒利到蜻蛉飛過都會即刻被切開而得名咩??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b68c489869ea708fd38675a748698289ab5e29","tid":2265772,"uid":213656,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:20:33.000Z","msg":"直接講9100會多啲人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865c19af2b4e2bd24fd054a577a18cf27eb53b63","tid":2265772,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:20:34.000Z","msg":"日本的刀係有排名之分,<br />\n例如咩十大妖刀,三大名刀等等.<br />\n視乎佢的罕有度, 出之邊個刀匠, 同埋性能等等<br />\n<br />\n如果以價值去排行<br />\n<br />\n村正妖刀---&gt;神息-----&gt;蜻蛉切----&gt; 葵紋越前康繼．禦神刀---&gt;虎徹銘刀"},{"pid":"e0fa5fbcabbafda9a40d31e10c6d161ee8cb47e8","tid":2265772,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"adbcc81ddcbdd99be32b7bc160cc1d70c3f03b7d","tid":2265772,"uid":228894,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:19:44.000Z","msg":"蜻蛉切個名唔係因為鋒利到蜻蛉飛過都會即刻被切開而得名咩??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:21:21.000Z","msg":"歷史不嬲有唔同講法,<br />\n例如點解李小龍叫李三腳,<br />\n有人話佢可以連續出三腳, 有人話佢可以凌空踢個波三次"},{"pid":"923430ce47dd7512463f73e33a87a1fb43573daf","tid":2265772,"uid":41292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:22:54.000Z","msg":"我只係知啲刀個名係整刀個條友<br />\n好似村正 正宗咁樣"},{"pid":"f73755bad422f7ee68272a92bd977884dd86febf","tid":2265772,"uid":353419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"617bb3836145f83f4907712965f3d7e449423a79","tid":2265772,"uid":113335,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:17:59.000Z","msg":"仲有魚神 正宗 菊一呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:信長學返黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=2php13v/96q0000sro2811r325s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2php13v%2F96q0000sro2811r325s.jpg&h=8dc5928c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實御神有好多把,佢唔係用來實戰, 係用來供奉係寺廟入面,  係由越前康繼打造, 點解咁出名呢, 因為佢俾德川家康賜予德川家葵紋, 目前供奉在尾張熱田神宮, 古代人認為御神刀有保護的作用"},{"pid":"43c22509d6bb751d76c7d31771e861719890d3b1","tid":2265772,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:26:39.000Z","msg":"細路果陣打咗十年八年信長<br />\n我都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867325774891261c4b14e8f9abead05ad8dffa62","tid":2265772,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"865c19af2b4e2bd24fd054a577a18cf27eb53b63","tid":2265772,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:20:34.000Z","msg":"日本的刀係有排名之分,<br />\n例如咩十大妖刀,三大名刀等等.<br />\n視乎佢的罕有度, 出之邊個刀匠, 同埋性能等等<br />\n<br />\n如果以價值去排行<br />\n<br />\n村正妖刀---&gt;神息-----&gt;蜻蛉切----&gt; 葵紋越前康繼．禦神刀---&gt;虎徹銘刀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:27:43.000Z","msg":"唔係正宗先最有價值咩"},{"pid":"fb880f095582e087270a464c1369ccec0e64af9e","tid":2265772,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"923430ce47dd7512463f73e33a87a1fb43573daf","tid":2265772,"uid":41292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:22:54.000Z","msg":"我只係知啲刀個名係整刀個條友<br />\n好似村正 正宗咁樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:28:19.000Z","msg":"其實日本古代的刀匠家族好多都有互相歷史關係,<br />\n舉個例子, 本多忠勝果把蜻蛉切, 係三河文珠派的刀匠, 而呢個派系的祖先,就係村正一族的分支"},{"pid":"2e7aaa05d0bd7b51667c691c162a439972d7d607","tid":2265772,"uid":303977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adbcc81ddcbdd99be32b7bc160cc1d70c3f03b7d","tid":2265772,"uid":228894,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:19:44.000Z","msg":"蜻蛉切個名唔係因為鋒利到蜻蛉飛過都會即刻被切開而得名咩??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:29:10.000Z","msg":"我都聽過呢個"},{"pid":"8e2de0453da2d2db1ab1bd894250cc48b032c432","tid":2265772,"uid":299263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:30:11.000Z","msg":"$# 屌地 鬼徹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLm等睇變信長post"},{"pid":"341d19a6700a1a4f845b98e089ae4211a2f572a4","tid":2265772,"uid":170399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:32:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢係日本最邪惡的一把刀，係江户時代由名匠村正一族打造，相傳得德川家康的爺爺，同織田家作戰果陣，俾家臣阿部彌七郎用呢把刀差啲砍死左，當時德川家康係受咀咒的刀，會吸食人血，可見古代日本人認為有啲刀變成成妖怪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n\b一把「江戶時代」先整既刀，點樣拎去「戰國時代」同織田家作戰呢？<br />\n<br />\n睇清楚D先發現自己係創意台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c8caeaac563cd8a4361a351c723671ec6202cd","tid":2265772,"uid":198824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T17:33:20.000Z","msg":"lm<br />\n利申:歷史系"},{"pid":"a29a59f481577dfd67187c80de8d7d2869b372ec","tid":2265772,"uid":353419,"li